Dear all,

Day 1.0 authors Shreyas Nair & Swapnil Basak will be in campus for a *one
hour information session* between *4pm *and *5pm,  23 Oct 2016 *in* MSB 242=
*

*Agenda*=E2=80=93 They will be talking about what it takes to crack an Inve=
stment
banking & consulting interview through their experience and provide
'fundae' on how to think about your preparation for the same. The hard copy
of the books will also be available there for sale.

*Brief *=E2=80=93 The book brings information and =E2=80=98fundaes=E2=80=99=
 for students appearing
for entry level interviews in consulting and investment banking. With no
clear guidance to help them to navigate through the recruitment cycle in
2015 the authors had to source and compile the information the hard way.
After getting recruited by leading management consulting and investment
banking firms, they decided to share their experiences and pass on tips and
tricks to future applicants. With 20 solved cases, more than 50 challenging
brainteasers, and first of its kind Investment Banking section, the Finance
and Investment Banking guide book is a definitive guide to the world of
Interview preparation.

Nishad, Shreyas & Swapnil - the authors - have all graduated from IIT
Madras in 2015 and are with The Boston Consulting Group, Mckinsey & Company
& Deutsche Bank respectively.

